data.title: 以至少 50 个字回答问题
data.content: "What personal achievement has been or would be the most meaningful to you? Why? Give specific reasons for your answer."
data.answer: The most meaningful achievement I have attained was my HSC. I was a very persistent person and before HSC, I clearly acknowledged my goal since Year 10 and it was to get into Actuarial Studies at UNSW. I knew it was difficult as HSC counted for the percentage, and getting a high state rank was hard. So I studied a lot and practiced a lot, and got band 6s for my Maths Extention 1 and 2, and finally made my dream come true. This was super meaningful as it gave me a chance to have the opportunity to do actuarial-related careers in the future.
